Label: MushBoy
Detail: It's a mushroom monster that loves dark and humid places. It has high attack power.

Label: EvilEye
Detail: It's a monster with captivating eyes. Its appearance might make it seem fragile- but it's actually extremely tough- making it suitable for defense.

Label: Fairy
Detail: It's a fairy monster- a pure crystallization of mana. It has a good balance in many areas- and high potential.

Label: Salamandra
Detail: It's a monster with a primitive form. It breathes fire to attack enemies. Its racial trait allows it to intimidate enemies and make them tire quickly.

Label: GreyHound
Detail: It's a friendly wolf-like monster. It's very brave and agile.

Detail: It's the evolved form of a slime- a Bloody Slime. It may look similar on the outside- but it has become considerably more powerful.

Label: FlameGolem
Detail: It's the evolved form of an Earth Golem- a Flame Golem. It's even sturdier and stronger.

Detail: They're a race that lives in nature and has a high affinity for mana. They have extensive knowledge about herbs and possess basic combat abilities.

Detail: They recently became an adventurer. As an adventurer- they're more interested in monsters and treasure than resources.

Label: Lower level herbs
Detail: It's a common herb. Although in small quantities- it contains mana and is popular since it can only be obtained from Dungeons.

Label: High level herbs
Detail: It's a quite rare herb. It's said to be used as an ingredient for high-grade potions.

Label: Mana radish
Detail: It's a radish containing mana. It's used as a top-grade food ingredient and in various other compounds.

Label: Common Rock
Detail: It's a common rock from the Dungeon. But it's a completely different material from rocks on the surface.

Label: Sandstone
Detail: It's a rock that easily crumbles into sand. It contains mana- making it easily moldable and mixable with water- giving it many uses.

Label: Hard rock
Detail: It's a sturdy rock. It's so tough that you'd need quite a bit of stamina to break it. It's popular as a construction material.

Label: Mana Ironstone
Detail: It's an iron ore containing high-purity iron. It's used for making weapons and various pieces of jewelry.

Label: Coal
Detail: It's a coal that ignites easily. Coal infused with mana has much greater heat output and duration- making it a premium fuel on the surface.

Label: Diamond
Detail: It's the extremely rare material- diamond. Its high mana purity makes it the core component of magical weapons. It's also extremely hard- making it difficult to mine.

Label: Golden Sword
Detail: It's a sword gilded with gold. It looks fancy- but is impractical for actual use and is decorative.

Label: Balance Sword
Detail: It's a sword with a suitable weight and balance for practical use.

Label: Exit
Detail: It designates the location of the entrance. \There can only be one entrance per floor. \If there is no entrance- one will automatically generate at the start.

Detail: Every 2 days- it supplies herbs to all activated floors. \Sometimes good herbs can appear!
